init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are now the Queen of the Bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You have the power to make bees do anything you want.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You can make them fight, make them build, make them dance, make them do anything you want.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked around and noticed that no one else was paying any attention to me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Bee looked at me and said "You are now the Queen of the Bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at the Bee and said "What do you mean i am the Queen of the Bees?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You are the Queen of the Bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at the Bee and said "I am not the Queen of the Bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at my reflection and noticed that my skin was now a light shade of yellow.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at my hands and noticed that they were now covered in yellow and black stripes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at the bee and said "What the heck is going on here?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee said "You are the Queen of the Bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee looked at me and said "I am here to serve you and make you happy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I will do anything you ask me to do."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at the bee and said "I want to go home."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They put me in a room and said "Your Majesty, this is your room.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You may go outside and explore the hive if you wish."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at the bees and said "I want to go home."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bees looked at me and said "Your Majesty, this is your home now.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are the Queen of the Bees."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bees looked at me and said "Your Majesty, we have prepared a feast for you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We have prepared the finest honey, royal jelly, and pollen for you."
